import re
from typing import List, Dict

def process_instructions(instructions: List[str], registers: Dict[str, int]) -> Dict[str, int]:
    i = 1
    while i < len(instructions):
        line = instructions[i]
        m1 = re.search('inc (\\w+)', line)
        if m1:
            register = m1.group(1)
            registers[register] += 1
            i += 1
            continue
        m2 = re.search('dec (\\w+)', line)
        if m2:
            register = m2.group(1)
            registers[register] -= 1
            i += 1
            continue
        m3 = re.search('jnz (\\w+) (-?\\d+)', line)
        if m3:
            (register, jump) = m3.groups()
            if registers[register] != 0:
                i += int(jump)
            else:
                i += 1
            continue
        m4 = re.search('jnz (\\w+) (\\w+)', line)
        if m4:
            (tester, jump) = m4.groups()
            if registers[tester] != 0:
                i += registers[jump]
            else:
                i += 1
            continue
    return registers
